---
title: Baked Cheesy Tomato Chicken with Golden Potatoes, Beans & Carrots
description: Keep your chicken breasts tender and full of flavour by baking them in a rich tomato sauce and covering the whole thing with Cheddar. With a melted, gooey top and lots of colourful veggies on the side, this chicken dinner will win over the whole family!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/cheesy-tomato-chicken-a0b07106.jpg
